! Catppuccin Theme for CodeMirror 6

A soothing pastel theme based on [[Catppuccin|https://github.com/catppuccin/catppuccin]].

!! Flavors

* `catppuccin-latte` - Light flavor
* `catppuccin-frappe` - Medium dark
* `catppuccin-macchiato` - Dark
* `catppuccin` / `catppuccin-mocha` - Darkest (default)

!! Available Theme Classes

| !Class | !Description |
| `cm6-theme-catppuccin` | Mocha (darkest, default) |
| `cm6-theme-catppuccin-mocha` | Same as above |
| `cm6-theme-catppuccin-macchiato` | Dark |
| `cm6-theme-catppuccin-frappe` | Medium dark |
| `cm6-theme-catppuccin-latte` | Light |
